{"lemma":"شِعار","slug":"شِعار","root":"ش.ع.ر","root_slug":"ش-ع-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ع-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":10},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22483","n22484"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%90%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%B1"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"password, watchword"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ensign"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"device"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mark, logo, token, sign"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"signal"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"badge, emblem"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"slogan, motto"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"battle cry, war cry"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of شَعْر (šaʕr)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of شَعَر (šaʕar)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʃi.ʕaːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22483","headword_ar":"شَعَارٌ","root":"$Er","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, Er-Riyáshee, S, A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaArN","text_ar":"شِعَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (As, ISh, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tangled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"luxuriant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant and dense, trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaArN","text_ar":"شِعَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Sh, T, K:) or (TA, but in the K “ and ”)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trees in land that is soft"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and depressed, between eminences,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where people alight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dahonaA='","text_ar":"دَهْنَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"warming themselves thereby in winter, and shading themselves thereby in summer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$oEarN","text_ar":"مَشْعَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) or this last signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any place in which are a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamar","text_ar":"خَمَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covert of trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aAEiru","text_ar":"مَشَاعِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN kaviyrapu Al$~aEaAri","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ كَثِيرَةُ الشَّعَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A land abounding in trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.]. (S.) ―         -b2-  See also the next paragraph, latter half."}],"source_refs":["As","ISh","K","Sh","T","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n22484","headword_ar":"شِعَارٌ","root":"$Er","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sign of people in war,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a journey"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) &c., (TA,) i. e. (Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a call"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of which to know one another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Mgh, Msb:) and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAr","text_ar":"شِعَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"of soldiers is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sign that is set up in order that a man may thereby know his companions:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAr","text_ar":"شِعَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"banners,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"standards,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of tribes. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brm","text_ar":"برم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) It is said in a trad. that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAr","text_ar":"شِعَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the Prophet in war was"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA manoSuwru A^amito A^amito","text_ar":"يَا مَنْصُورُ اَمِتْ اَمِتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O Mansoor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a proper name of a man, meaning “ aided ” &c.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kill thou, kill thou"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And it is said that he appointed the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAr","text_ar":"شِعَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the refugees on the day of Bedr to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yAbaniY Eabodi Alr~aHom`ni","text_ar":"يابَنِى عَبْدِ الرَّحْمٰنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$EAr","text_ar":"شعار"},{"kind":"text","text":"of El-Khazraj,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yA baniY Eabodi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"يا بَنِى عَبْدِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and that of El-Ows,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA baniY Eubayodi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"يَا بَنِى عُبَيْدِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and their"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$EAr","text_ar":"شعار"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the day of El-Ahzáb,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H`m= laA yunoSaruwna","text_ar":"حٰم= لَا يُنْصَرُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thunder;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Tekmileh, K;) as being a sign of rain. (TK.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAru AlHaj~i","text_ar":"شِعَارُ الحَجِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The religious rites and ceremonies of the pilgrimage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the signs thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) and, (TA,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$aEaAy^iru","text_ar":"الشَعَايِرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the practices of the pilgrimage, and whatever is appointed as a sign of obedience to God;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, * TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as the halting"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at Mount 'Arafát"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the circuiting"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"around the Kaabeh"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEoY","text_ar":"سَعْى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tripping to and fro between Es-Safà and El-Marweh"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the throwing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the pebbles at Minè"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the sacrifice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEiyrapN","text_ar":"شَعِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaArapN","text_ar":"شِعَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$oErN","text_ar":"مَشْعرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaArN","text_ar":"شِعَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEiyrapN","text_ar":"شَعِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEaAy^iru","text_ar":"شَعَايِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning as expl. above; (As, S, Msb;) or, as some say, the sing. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaArapN","text_ar":"شِعَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (As, S:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEiyrapN","text_ar":"شَعِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaArapN","text_ar":"شِعَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", by some written ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEaArapN","text_ar":"شَعَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$oEarN","text_ar":"مَشْعَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the performance"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of religious rites and ceremonies of the pilgrimage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"expl. in the K by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEoZamuhaA","text_ar":"مُعْظَمُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawoDiEuhaA","text_ar":"مَوْضِعُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aAEiru","text_ar":"مَشَاعِرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaj~i","text_ar":"الحَجِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEaAy^iru","text_ar":"شَعَايِرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEaAlim","text_ar":"مَعَالِم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"characteristic practices"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the pilgrimage, to which God has invited, and the performance of which He has commanded;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alma$aAEiru","text_ar":"المَشَاعِرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEaAy^iru","text_ar":"شَعَايِرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all those religious services which God has appointed to us as signs; as the halting"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at Mount 'Arafát"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEoY","text_ar":"سَعْى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tripping to and fro between Es-Safà and El-Marweh"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the sacrificing of victims:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the rites and ceremonies of the pilgrimage, and the places where those rites and ceremonies are performed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in v. 2 and xxii. 33;) among which places are Es-Safà and El-Marweh, they being thus expressly termed; (Kur ii. 153;) and so accord. to Fr in the Kur v. 2: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the obligatory statutes"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordinances of God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in v. 2:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the religion of God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in v. 2 and xxii. 33:) the camels or cows or bulls destined to be sacrificed at Mekkeh are also said in the Kur xxii. 37, to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino $aEaAy^iri A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"مِنْ شَعَايِرِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the signs of the religion of God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd and Jel:) and [hence the sing.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEiyrapN","text_ar":"شَعِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [sometimes]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bull that is brought to Mekkeh for sacrifice;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is marked in the manner expl. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oEara","text_ar":"اَشْعَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEaAy^iru","text_ar":"شَعَايِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is its pl.; (K;) and is also pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaArN","text_ar":"شِعَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and the [festival called the]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eiyd","text_ar":"عِيد"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to be a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAr","text_ar":"شِعَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEaAy^ir","text_ar":"شَعَايِر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sign of the signs of the religion"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of El-Islám. (Msb.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAru Ald~ami","text_ar":"شِعَارُ الدَّمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to mean (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The piece of rag:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the vulva:"},{"kind":"text","text":"because each is a thing that indicates the existence of blood. (Mgh.)       -A2-  Also The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"innermost garment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garment that is next the body;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garment that is next the hair of the body, under the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"divaAr","text_ar":"دِثَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEaArN","text_ar":"شَعَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) but this is strange: (TA:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oEirapN","text_ar":"اَشْعِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEurN","text_ar":"شُعُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"labisa $iEaAra Alham~i","text_ar":"لَبِسَ شِعَارَ الهَمِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He involved himself in anxiety"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEala Alxawofa $iEaArahu","text_ar":"جَعَلَ الخَوْفَ شِعَارَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made fear to be"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his innermost garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"], by closely cleaving to it. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drE","text_ar":"درع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [Hence, also,] it is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humu Al$~iEaAru duwna Ald~ivaAri","text_ar":"هُمُ الشِّعَارُ دُونَ الدِّثَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are near in respect of love:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in a trad., relating to the Ansár,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anotumu Al$~iEaAru waAln~aAsu Ald~ivaAru","text_ar":"اَنْتُمُ الشِّعَارُ وَالنَّاسُ الدِّثَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ye are the special and close friends"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the people in general are the less near in friendship"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse-cloth; a covering for a horse to protect him from the cold."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing with which wine"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. while in the vat]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is protected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preserved from injury:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K: [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxamoru","text_ar":"الخَمْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the reading in the CK, the author of the TK has read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxumuru","text_ar":"الخُمُرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(and thus I find the word written in my MS. copy of the K) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxumoru","text_ar":"الخُمْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", pls. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlximaAru","text_ar":"الخِمَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and Freytag has followed his example: but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxamoru","text_ar":"الخَمْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the right reading, as is shown by what here follows:]) so in the saying of El-Akhtal,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"fakaf~a Alr~iyHa waAlA^anodaA='a EanohaA\n                      \n                     \n                        mina Alz~arajuwni duwnahumaA Al$~iEaAru"},{"kind":"text","text":"[evidently describing wine, and app. meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$EAr","text_ar":"شعار"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the wine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~iEaAru mina Alz~arajuwna","text_ar":"الشِّعَارُ مِنَ الزَّرَجُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAru Alz~arajuwni","text_ar":"شِعَارُ الزَّرَجُونِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) while yet in the vat,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervening as an obstacle to them, kept off the wind and the rains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dews,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"day-dews, from it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, the wine]. (L.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEaArN","text_ar":"شَعَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","A","Mgh","L","As","Zj"]}]}}